More light than you can handle! Also: This is in beta state. Don't judge me!


*******
Install
*******

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install merlict


***************
Minimal example
***************

.. code-block:: python

    import merlict

    scenery = merlict.c89.wrapper.Server(path="merlict/tests/resources/segmented_reflector.tar")
    scenery.view()


